Plants are known for having senses and personality that we humans cannot perceive. Purpose is to use tech to bring that connection to nature.
Live Plant consists of a natural plant having each leaf attatched to an alligator clip that is each connected to a tone, allowing it to play sound upon impact.
Different sections of the leaf plays different tone, from a variety of 6, bringing the apsect of life into the plant as their personality is represented in their leaves.
This is an interactive work intended to highlight humans dependence of the environment. Through interaction with nature, one may witness that connection.
